Deploying example (counter) contract:

```
push_contract base-account-keys 100000 0 ./Counter 
```

Compile a 'production' contract:
```
likelib> compile git/supplike/blockchain/contracts/SupplyChain.sol
Compiled contracts:
	SupplyChain
	SupplyChainFactory
```

```
encode SupplyChainFactory "constructor()"
```



push_contract base-account-keys 1000000 0 SupplyChainFactory 

Production contract:
```
3bjrbaMkvWyDaxP5YQVZ337usG6D
```

Running a node:
```
sudo docker run --name likelib11 -d  -v "${PWD}/supplike/blockchain:/opt/lkl/git" -p 20203:20203 -p 50051:50051 -p 50052:50052 -p 50053:50053 heshuby/utonhack:2020-07-20-private ./node
```
